1. *Časa* je polomljena na stolu. (The glass is broken on the table.)
2. Drago mi je što smo proveli *časa* zajedno. (I'm glad we spent time together.)
3. Molim vas, donesite mi *časa* vode. (Please bring me a glass of water.)
4. Nema više *časa* za razgovor. (There's no more time for talking.)
5. *Časa* je bila puna do vrha. (The glass was filled to the brim.)
6. Moram kupiti novu *časa* za kafu. (I need to buy a new coffee cup.)
7. *Časa* je pala sa stola i razbila se. (The glass fell off the table and broke.)
8. U ovoj trgovini imaju veliki izbor *časa* i tanjira. (This store has a large selection of glasses and plates.)
9. Da li si video moju *časa* negde u sobi? (Have you seen my glass somewhere in the room?)
10. *Časa* se tresla u njenoj ruci dok je pila čaj. (The glass shook in her hand as she drank tea.)

Note: The word "časa" can be translated to "glass" or "cup" depending on the context.